Simple sample code for the Raspberry Pi e-ink YouTube stats project.

This code uses the YouTube API and a Pimoroni InkypHAT to display statistics from your youtube channel.

The script is configured to use a switch to choose between displaying Total Views or Total Subscribers.

Read the full write-up and build instructions at: 

Instructables: https://www.instructables.com/id/1970s-E-Ink-YouTube-Counter

Hackster: https://www.hackster.io/martin-mander/1970s-e-ink-youtube-counter-9bd195

YouTube: https://youtu.be/jKEZ2S3fj38 and https://youtu.be/tz_xByoevCQ
